{"tid":641416,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日日淨係識撚狗公J淫腳，你班連登仔日日俾人當豬咁撚都唔知","createTime":"2018-04-25T03:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T05:29:24.000Z","uid":149792,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6341225757cb6cddf68d6115f002ab559b1d41b8","tid":641416,"uid":149792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"王光亞：叫「結束一黨專政」違法　應不可參選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/113557_7ede707dfe6fd884add6db15ca10f44d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F113557_7ede707dfe6fd884add6db15ca10f44d.jpg&h=729a3209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地修訂《憲法》後，叫「結束一黨專政」口號的人能否參選立法會，近日引起關注。正在北京的港澳辦前主任王光亞稱「應該不可以（參選）」，因為這樣違反國家《憲法》，是違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n王光亞指出，《憲法》規定內地政治體制是中國共產黨領導，雖然並非「一黨專政」，但形容有關口號「針對性很明顯」。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大憲法和法律委員會主任委員李飛則表示不評論，因他已不再分管港澳事務。<br />\n<br />\n2016年：「港獨、建國」違反憲法，不能參選<br />\n2017年：「民主自決」違反憲法，不能參選<br />\n2018年：「結束一黨專政」違反憲法，不能參選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連豬訓醒未啊, 如果撚共產黨好似撚狗公咁撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港就有希望喇  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9996c246bb01e4e0f0145a1a056f33a329bcd1a5","tid":641416,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/jbK6ioUckjrbZ89vci/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FjbK6ioUckjrbZ89vci%2Fgiphy.gif&h=ca000b15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb9f90cbe3019d3826debaf25697f70ffa3128c2","tid":641416,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"班小朋友有機打有網上就ok"},{"pid":"a56a67b30ddfb54e31d509fb80173faf4e060e73","tid":641416,"uid":17284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"